Files on this directory belong to project 1 of CS525. Such files are:

\
|--readme: this file
|--install: installation details
|--makefile: GNU Make file for building and testing.
|
|--range-serial.c: serial implementation of part A.
|--range-mpi-ppv1.c: parallel implementation v1 of part A.
|--range-mpi-ppv2.c: parallel implementation v2 of part A.
|--sort_aggr-serial.c: serial implementation of part B.
|--sort_aggr-mpi.c: parallel implementation 2nd option of part B.
|
|--aux.c: auxiliary functions.
|--headers.h: header file for common libraries.
|
|--input_range: test data for range programs.
|--input_sort_aggr: test data for sort-aggregate programs.
|
|--{0-N}.log: log files for parallel debugging.

In order to build the source code, use:
make build

In order to run the default tests, use:
make run

make clean will delete temporary files and binaries.